Bogomoljke.

479
00:39:03,265 --> 00:39:07,308
Znaš kako se pare?
Mužjak priđe ženki,

480
00:39:07,393 --> 00:39:09,350
ona mu odgrize glavu;

481
00:39:09,479 --> 00:39:12,230
ostatak tijela mu je
i dalje u parenju.

482
00:39:12,314 --> 00:39:17,769
Kad završe, ona ga
pojede cijeloga.

483
00:39:19,362 --> 00:39:21,604
Bako, imamo društvo.

484
00:39:21,822 --> 00:39:24,230
Hoćeš li jesti s nama?

485
00:39:26,869 --> 00:39:29,027
Posluži se.
- Hvala.

486
00:39:34,374 --> 00:39:37,044
Zakasnile smo na
skup u Des Moinsu.

487
00:39:37,711 --> 00:39:40,036
Krenemo li u petak,
možda ih ulovimo

488
00:39:40,173 --> 00:39:44,040
u Colorado Springsu.
Jesi li bio tamo?

489
00:39:44,634 --> 00:39:46,342
Nisam.

490
00:39:46,636 --> 00:39:48,463
Zacijelo je lijepo.

491
00:39:48,596 --> 00:39:53,423
Sigurno vam je grozno
što čamite u Endori.

492
00:39:53,559 --> 00:39:57,093
Mjesto ko i svako
drugo. - Misliš?

493
00:39:58,479 --> 00:40:00,271
Ona najbolje zna.

494
00:40:00,773 --> 00:40:03,858
Nema gdje nije bila -

495
00:40:03,985 --> 00:40:06,108
i u mjestima za koja
nisam znala da postoje!

496
00:40:06,196 --> 00:40:08,899
Ja sam svjetska djevojka.

497
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:15,321
Ja sam cijeli život
bila u istom mjestu.

498
00:40:15,912 --> 00:40:17,989
Zašto, nije važno.

499
00:40:18,123 --> 00:40:21,456
Ona me natjerala
da se počnem kretati.

500
00:40:21,543 --> 00:40:24,578
I sad nigdje ne može
dugo ostati!

501
00:40:26,671 --> 00:40:29,838
Ona je najpametnija
i najljepša na svijetu.

502
00:40:30,092 --> 00:40:32,215
Nije li lijepa?

503
00:40:32,386 --> 00:40:34,177
Nije li lijepa?

504
00:40:37,556 --> 00:40:41,389
Oprosti, njoj je
ljepota opsesija...

505
00:40:41,477 --> 00:40:43,552
Primijetio sam.

506
00:40:43,728 --> 00:40:47,773
Mene ne zanima
izvanjska ljepota

507
00:40:48,024 --> 00:40:50,693
jer ne traje dugo.

508
00:40:50,818 --> 00:40:52,397
Točno.

509
00:40:52,612 --> 00:40:55,363
S vremenom, lice ti
postane puno bora,

510
00:40:55,447 --> 00:40:56,905
kosa ti posijedi,

511
00:40:57,074 --> 00:41:00,489
cice se objese... Pa što?

512
00:41:00,951 --> 00:41:03,408
Važno je ono što radiš.

513
00:41:04,163 --> 00:41:06,203
Zar ne?
- Svakako.

514
00:41:07,083 --> 00:41:09,242
Onda, što želiš raditi?

515
00:41:10,170 --> 00:41:13,704
Ne znam. Ovdje nema
mnogo izbora...

516
00:41:15,257 --> 00:41:19,337
Razmisli što ljudi
ovdje najčešće rade.

517
00:41:24,306 --> 00:41:25,800
Hvala.

518
00:41:26,559 --> 00:41:28,349
Bilo mi je drago.

519
00:41:30,688 --> 00:41:32,097
Budi pristojna.

520
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:38,519
Zdravo.

521
00:41:46,869 --> 00:41:50,617
Ti uzmi moj, a
ja ću tvoj, može?

522
00:41:53,875 --> 00:41:56,661
Onaj na vrhu je dobar.

523
00:41:56,794 --> 00:41:59,284
Ne, hoćemo velike!

524
00:41:59,421 --> 00:42:03,205
Dobro... - Dođi, idemo.
- Hoću veliki...

525
00:42:03,717 --> 00:42:05,839
Molim te, mama!

526
00:42:06,176 --> 00:42:09,047
Hoćemo velike!
- Dobro.

527
00:42:10,723 --> 00:42:12,099
Mijenja se.

528
00:42:13,391 --> 00:42:16,309
To mi se sviđa
kod zalaska sunca:

529
00:42:16,436 --> 00:42:19,770
Mijenja se, sporo,
tebi ispred očiju.

530
00:42:25,695 --> 00:42:27,521
Volim nebo.

531
00:42:28,698 --> 00:42:32,280
Beskrajno je.

532
00:42:33,326 --> 00:42:36,281
Da, veliko je. Jako veliko.

533
00:42:36,412 --> 00:42:39,330
Veliko nije prava riječ;

534
00:42:39,499 --> 00:42:45,418
premalena je da
opiše veličinu neba.

535
00:42:50,633 --> 00:42:52,211
Što je?

536
00:42:54,053 --> 00:42:57,008
Moram ići. Obiteljska obveza.

537
00:42:58,015 --> 00:43:01,218
Da te odvezem do
grada, ili...?

538
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:04,477
Ne. Ostat ću ovdje sjediti.

539
00:43:08,441 --> 00:43:10,101
Mogao bih se vratiti.

540
00:43:10,277 --> 00:43:12,648
Mogao bih...
- Stvarno?

541
00:43:12,778 --> 00:43:15,529
Bit ćeš ovdje?
- Hoću.

542
00:43:15,656 --> 00:43:17,199
Sjedit ću ovdje.

543
00:43:17,324 --> 00:43:19,363
Brzo ću se vratiti.

544
00:43:23,079 --> 00:43:25,949
Gilberte...
- Idemo, stari.

545
00:43:26,082 --> 00:43:27,956
Moramo ići.

546
00:43:30,128 --> 00:43:32,084
Gdje je patka?
- Evo je.

547
00:43:32,213 --> 00:43:36,257
Ne vidim je. Nađi je.
Gdje je otišla?

548
00:43:36,425 --> 00:43:38,252
Gdje je patka?
- Skrila se.

549
00:43:38,385 --> 00:43:41,137
Nađi patku. - Nemam
vremena za igru.

550
00:43:42,388 --> 00:43:45,472
Patkice... - Tako
treba. Znaš što?

551
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:47,800
Velik si ti dečko.

552
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:50,515
Jako si velik.
- Velik dečko.

553
00:43:50,646 --> 00:43:54,809
Mogao bi se i sam
kupati, samo da hoćeš.

554
00:43:55,109 --> 00:43:56,816
Misliš da bi mogao?

555
00:43:56,943 --> 00:43:59,730
Ja sam velik dečko.
- Da. Budi velik dečko.

556
00:43:59,861 --> 00:44:02,648
Uzmi ovo. Sve operi.

557
00:44:02,781 --> 00:44:06,909
Ručnici su ovdje.
Ogrtač ti je ovdje.

558
00:44:07,118 --> 00:44:10,451
Veliki će se dečko
sam oprati.

559
00:44:10,580 --> 00:44:12,122
Moram ići.

560
00:44:14,959 --> 00:44:16,702
Propustio si ga.

561
00:44:16,919 --> 00:44:20,287
Koga? - Zalazak
sunca. - Stvarno?

562
00:44:20,463 --> 00:44:22,172
Bio je divan.

563
00:44:28,472 --> 00:44:31,175
Voljela bih vidjeti
gdje živiš.

564
00:44:31,599 --> 00:44:33,426
Ne bi.

565
00:44:33,517 --> 00:44:36,885
Pokaži mi. Krenimo.

566
00:44:44,109 --> 00:44:47,359
Moji su se rastali
kad sam bila mala.

567
00:44:48,072 --> 00:44:52,235
Malo sam s mamom, malo
s tatom. Stalno putuju.

568
00:44:53,452 --> 00:44:56,618
No tako je dobro.
To je moj život.

569
00:45:00,625 --> 00:45:02,533
Mi nikamo ne idemo.

570
00:45:02,793 --> 00:45:05,366
Volio bih, ali...

571
00:45:06,505 --> 00:45:09,078
Moja je mama vezana za kuću.

572
00:45:10,426 --> 00:45:13,129
Vezana je preslaba riječ;

573
00:45:13,261 --> 00:45:15,384
bolje je reći prikovana.

574
00:45:15,596 --> 00:45:19,843
Kako to misliš?
- Evo, to je moja kuća.

575
00:45:23,062 --> 00:45:25,019
Nevjerojatno...

576
00:45:25,229 --> 00:45:28,764
Kako izgleda malena
odavde, uzevši u obzir

577
00:45:30,067 --> 00:45:32,439
opseg onoga unutra.

578
00:45:39,994 --> 00:45:44,122
Jesi li kad vidjela
na TV nasukana kita?

579
00:45:45,582 --> 00:45:48,832
Moja je mama točno takva.

580
00:45:53,588 --> 00:45:55,297
A tvoj tata?

581
00:45:56,216 --> 00:45:58,374
O tome ćemo
drugom prilikom...

582
00:46:13,397 --> 00:46:15,722
Bilo mi je lijepo.

583
00:46:17,818 --> 00:46:19,277
Znam.

584
00:46:23,531 --> 00:46:24,907
Laku noć.

585
00:47:10,199 --> 00:47:11,609
O, ne!

586
00:47:13,576 --> 00:47:15,236
Joj, Arnie...

587
00:47:15,411 --> 00:47:17,488
Oprosti...

588
00:47:20,625 --> 00:47:23,032
Jesi li dobro? Dobro si...

589
00:47:25,837 --> 00:47:27,497
Utoplit ćemo te.

590
00:47:28,298 --> 00:47:30,255
Oprosti mi, Arnie.

591
00:47:30,466 --> 00:47:34,085
Oprosti...

592
00:47:34,387 --> 00:47:37,008
Bi li mi tko objasnio?

593
00:47:37,181 --> 00:47:39,387
Gilbert je zadužen za kupanje.

594
00:47:39,515 --> 00:47:43,892
Mogao sam se utopiti!

595
00:47:44,062 --> 00:47:46,848
Ne želimo to.

596
00:47:46,981 --> 00:47:49,270
Mogao si, ali nisi, dušo.

597
00:47:49,359 --> 00:47:51,600
Neću se više kupati.

598
00:47:51,902 --> 00:47:56,398
Je li previše što želim da
doživi 18. rođendan? - Ne.

599
00:47:57,616 --> 00:48:01,315
Gotovo! - Što se događa
s tobom, Gilberte?

600
00:48:01,453 --> 00:48:03,528
Gdje ti je glava?

601
00:48:03,704 --> 00:48:06,326
Gilberte?
- Žao mi je.

602
00:48:06,457 --> 00:48:08,782
To mi ništa ne znači.

603
00:48:08,960 --> 00:48:12,743
Moraš se više truditi.
- Moraš se više truditi.

604
00:48:15,131 --> 00:48:16,460
Šefe,

605
00:48:16,633 --> 00:48:18,506
ovo je ispravna cijena?

606
00:48:18,926 --> 00:48:20,504
Jest.

607
00:48:21,054 --> 00:48:24,920
Trebala bi biti viša.
- Možda u Foodlandu.

608
00:48:25,099 --> 00:48:29,226
Mi uvijek imamo
razumne cijene. - Uzmi.

609
00:48:32,398 --> 00:48:35,647
Gilberte, isporuka.
- Zvučalo je hitno.

610
00:48:46,994 --> 00:48:49,614
Idite se van igrati.

611
00:48:49,746 --> 00:48:52,118
Ali... - Smjesta!

612
00:49:00,880 --> 00:49:02,789
Zdravo, Betty.

613
00:49:05,134 --> 00:49:09,428
Nazovi mi ovaj broj;
ruke su mi...

614
00:49:09,639 --> 00:49:11,678
Odmah.

615
00:49:11,849 --> 00:49:12,762
Kako si?

616
00:49:12,850 --> 00:49:15,553
Dobro. - Vidjela
sam te sinoć.

617
00:49:17,270 --> 00:49:18,813
Tko je ta djevojka?

618
00:49:19,689 --> 00:49:21,099
Zvoni.

619
00:49:22,025 --> 00:49:23,400
Trenutak...

620
00:49:25,403 --> 00:49:28,272
Fino je. Kušaj.

621
00:49:28,573 --> 00:49:29,817
Jest... Zvoni.

622
00:49:29,989 --> 00:49:31,400
Samo malo.

623
00:49:32,658 --> 00:49:35,364
Ken Carver,
Osiguranje Carver.

624
00:49:40,833 --> 00:49:43,370
G. Carver?
- Tko je to?

625
00:49:44,294 --> 00:49:47,378
Gilbert.
- Gilberte!

626
00:49:48,214 --> 00:49:52,129
Već sam digao ruke
od tebe. - Da?

627
00:49:52,259 --> 00:49:54,881
Ne krivi me...
- Ne. Ne!

628
00:49:55,054 --> 00:49:58,338
Stalno te zovem, a ti ništa.

629
00:49:58,432 --> 00:50:01,136
Evo, sad zovem...
- Sretna godišnjica.

630
00:50:01,268 --> 00:50:03,011
Nemojmo preko telefona.

631
00:50:03,144 --> 00:50:05,183
Moramo se naći
licem u lice.

632
00:50:07,106 --> 00:50:09,146
Danas ti je sretan dan;

633
00:50:09,317 --> 00:50:12,602
imam slobodan termin.
Dođi sada.

634
00:50:15,613 --> 00:50:17,440
To znači da?

635
00:50:20,327 --> 00:50:23,281
Čekam te, Gilberte.
- 'Đenja.

636
00:50:25,206 --> 00:50:28,325
Hoćeš da me ubije?
To hoćeš?!

637
00:50:28,458 --> 00:50:31,827
Samo se igram. Ti se
ne želiš igrati?

638
00:50:32,003 --> 00:50:34,708
Ovo je ludost... Moram ići.

639
00:50:34,797 --> 00:50:37,336
Ne moraš.
- Moram.

640
00:50:40,595 --> 00:50:42,883
Zbog one cure, zar ne?

641
00:50:43,222 --> 00:50:46,507
Zbog tvoga muža!
Čeka me u svom uredu.

642
00:50:46,892 --> 00:50:49,133
Odeš li sada...

643
00:50:50,228 --> 00:50:52,896
Da se nisi usudio otići!

644
00:51:16,960 --> 00:51:19,416
Doimaš se malo
živčanim, Gilberte.

645
00:51:20,379 --> 00:51:23,001
Na tvom mjestu,
i ja bih bio.

646
00:51:23,716 --> 00:51:27,334
Bio bih u potpunoj panici.

647
00:51:28,471 --> 00:51:31,175
Pregledao sam tvoj dosje.

648
00:51:31,348 --> 00:51:34,717
Nemaš zdravstveno osiguranje,

649
00:51:34,810 --> 00:51:38,177
ni u slučaju nesreće,
ni životno...

650
00:51:41,566 --> 00:51:43,688
Što ako ti se nešto dogodi?

651
00:51:45,695 --> 00:51:48,980
Nešto nepredviđeno?

652
00:51:49,155 --> 00:51:51,361
Nešto neočekivano?

653
00:51:52,742 --> 00:51:54,984
Prometna nesreća, recimo.

654
00:51:55,119 --> 00:51:56,862
Što bi tvoja obitelj?

655
00:51:57,955 --> 00:52:00,706
Misliš li ikad na obitelj?

656
00:52:01,917 --> 00:52:05,119
Ne misli samo na sebe.
Misli na njih!

657
00:52:06,422 --> 00:52:09,292
Ne bi htio da
ostanu bez ičega.

658
00:52:10,092 --> 00:52:11,799
Ken Carver.

659
00:52:12,719 --> 00:52:14,959
Može li to pričekati?

660
00:52:17,097 --> 00:52:19,767
Betty... Smiri se.

661
00:52:20,225 --> 00:52:23,594
Smiri se... Ne.

662
00:52:28,650 --> 00:52:32,148
Ne, ne...

663
00:52:40,451 --> 00:52:43,368
Ne... Smiri se.

664
00:52:43,538 --> 00:52:45,446
Dolazim.

665
00:52:49,167 --> 00:52:52,417
Kućni problemi, razumiješ...

666
00:52:53,630 --> 00:52:56,085
Kvragu, Betty ima auto.

667
00:52:56,256 --> 00:52:58,249
Možeš li me odvesti?

668
00:53:19,944 --> 00:53:22,233
Zaboga, Betty!

669
00:53:22,406 --> 00:53:24,398
Što se zbiva?!

670
00:53:24,533 --> 00:53:28,909
Todd! Doug! Što se događa?!

671
00:53:30,829 --> 00:53:32,622
No krasno!

672
00:53:33,915 --> 00:53:35,659
Kolačići!

673
00:53:35,751 --> 00:53:40,328
Dečki, kušajmo
mamine kolačiće.

674
00:53:40,880 --> 00:53:42,624
Super.

675
00:53:45,969 --> 00:53:47,794
Sve je u redu.

676
00:53:49,054 --> 00:53:51,805
Zlato, dobri su.

677
00:53:53,517 --> 00:53:56,387
Malo zagorjeli odozgo,
ali vrlo ukusni.

678
00:53:56,603 --> 00:53:58,226
Sjajni su.

679
00:53:59,355 --> 00:54:02,723
Dečki, kušajte
mamine kolačiće.

680
00:54:02,900 --> 00:54:04,559
Baš su dobri.

681
00:54:04,692 --> 00:54:08,393
Hajde, mami za
ljubav. - Neću.

682
00:54:08,654 --> 00:54:10,279
Uzmite...

683
00:54:10,532 --> 00:54:12,689
Barem jednoga.

684
00:54:13,326 --> 00:54:16,611
Mogla sam imati
bilo kojeg muškarca.

685
00:54:17,330 --> 00:54:18,491
Ali...

686
00:54:18,622 --> 00:54:21,706
Dođi, Doug!
- Izabrala sam tebe.

687
00:54:21,833 --> 00:54:23,114
Tebe.

688
00:54:23,293 --> 00:54:25,120
Ovo je bazen!

689
00:54:25,252 --> 00:54:27,542
Voda je unutra.

690
00:54:27,672 --> 00:54:29,331
Dođi.

691
00:54:29,924 --> 00:54:32,628
Uđite u bazen.

692
00:54:33,385 --> 00:54:35,424
Uđi u bazen.

693
00:54:36,179 --> 00:54:38,505
Zašto?

694
00:54:39,683 --> 00:54:42,553
Vidi, prava voda...

695
00:54:43,394 --> 00:54:47,226
Sve vam pružam...
- Jer sam

696
00:54:47,357 --> 00:54:50,440
znala da ćeš uvijek
biti ovdje.

697
00:54:51,360 --> 00:54:53,482
Da nećeš otići.

698
00:54:53,611 --> 00:54:57,312
Imate bazen, trampolin;
što još hoćete?!

699
00:54:57,449 --> 00:55:00,366
Što još, zaboga?!

700
00:55:02,452 --> 00:55:06,402
Sine, uđi u bazen!

701
00:55:06,539 --> 00:55:10,702
Svi ćemo se zabavljati.

702
00:55:10,877 --> 00:55:15,789
Trudim se koliko
mogu! Ne mogu više!

703
00:55:15,924 --> 00:55:18,959
Pružam vam sve što mogu!

704
00:55:52,706 --> 00:55:56,834
Arnie se mora
okupati. - Neću!

705
00:55:57,960 --> 00:56:01,081
Nije li vrijeme
da se Arnie okupa?

706
00:56:01,214 --> 00:56:05,922
Pusti, neka smrdi.
- Neću se kupati!

707
00:56:06,719 --> 00:56:08,758
Znate li g. Carvera?

708
00:56:10,513 --> 00:56:11,924
Mrtav je.

709
00:56:40,456 --> 00:56:43,493
Što je bilo?
- Utopio se.

710
00:56:44,585 --> 00:56:47,041
Šališ se?!
- Ne. U onome!

711
00:56:49,673 --> 00:56:51,713
U dječjem bazenu! Ne kužim.

712
00:56:53,093 --> 00:56:56,427
U tri kapi vode! Čudno...

713
00:56:56,763 --> 00:56:58,721
Utopio se!

714
00:57:08,274 --> 00:57:10,515
Imao je infarkt;

715
00:57:10,901 --> 00:57:14,685
glava mu je klonula,
koljena otkazala -

716
00:57:14,988 --> 00:57:17,193
pao je

717
00:57:18,574 --> 00:57:20,483
licem u vodu.

718
00:57:20,659 --> 00:57:22,984
Bio je već mrtav
kad ga je našla.

719
00:57:23,162 --> 00:57:25,284
To se ne zna...

720
00:57:25,414 --> 00:57:29,411
Ne, ja sam vidio tijelo.

721
00:57:29,543 --> 00:57:31,084
Pripremio sam ga.

722
00:57:31,169 --> 00:57:33,838
Znam o čemu govorim. Vidio bih

723
00:57:33,922 --> 00:57:37,207
da se radilo o kakvoj borbi.

724
00:57:37,300 --> 00:57:39,836
Ubila ga je.
- Nije.

725
00:57:40,010 --> 00:57:41,587
Što ti misliš?

726
00:57:41,762 --> 00:57:44,050
Ja... Ne znam.

727
00:57:44,348 --> 00:57:46,055
Moguće je.

728
00:57:46,474 --> 00:57:50,307
Radi se o tisućama
i tisućama dolara.

729
00:57:50,436 --> 00:57:53,222
Ne bi morala raditi...
- Čak i da htjela...

730
00:57:53,355 --> 00:57:56,938
...do kraja života.
- Da vidiš nekoga

731
00:57:57,109 --> 00:58:00,858
s glavom u bazenu, nepomična,

732
00:58:00,945 --> 00:58:04,528
ili da se malko
pomiče, ovako,

733
00:58:04,616 --> 00:58:07,367
što on nije, ali...
- Otkud znaš?

734
00:58:07,493 --> 00:58:11,442
Pao je zbog siline infarkta.

735
00:58:11,539 --> 00:58:14,374
Dakle, nema ništa
sumnjivo? - Nema.

736
00:58:14,500 --> 00:58:16,955
Eno one cure!

737
00:58:17,044 --> 00:58:19,580
Gilberte, ona cura!

738
00:58:20,838 --> 00:58:26,176
...Čak i da jest... - Nije
ga ustrijelila, ali...

739
00:58:26,343 --> 00:58:27,623
Bog.

740
00:58:27,803 --> 00:58:29,763
...to se moglo
očekivati...

741
00:58:29,763 --> 00:58:31,886
Idemo se igrati.

742
00:58:34,017 --> 00:58:36,685
Kako si? - Dobro.

743
00:58:36,935 --> 00:58:39,059
Molim te!
- Dobro.

744
00:58:39,230 --> 00:58:41,686
Igrat ćemo se!

745
00:58:41,774 --> 00:58:43,849
Možeš li me odvesti?

746
00:58:49,071 --> 00:58:50,446
To je to?

747
00:58:51,574 --> 00:58:53,281
Čini se.

748
00:58:56,787 --> 00:58:58,245
Čarobni dio.

749
00:59:04,127 --> 00:59:05,751
Čarobni dio?

750
00:59:07,671 --> 00:59:10,874
Kakav čarobni dio?

751
00:59:16,389 --> 00:59:19,887
Možemo... - Bako, dio
je stigao. - Hvala.

752
00:59:19,975 --> 00:59:22,050
Idemo se igrati?

753
00:59:23,645 --> 00:59:25,636
Možemo se igrati skrivača...

754
00:59:25,771 --> 00:59:27,479
Skrivača...

755
00:59:27,605 --> 00:59:31,438
Gilberte... Možeš li
mi pomoći? - Probajte.

756
00:59:37,989 --> 00:59:39,270
Trenutak.

757
00:59:42,452 --> 00:59:43,828
Pokušajte.

758
00:59:53,338 --> 00:59:54,880
Ne znam...

759
00:59:55,088 --> 00:59:57,045
Ni ja...

760
00:59:58,050 --> 00:59:59,379
Baš čudno.

761
00:59:59,719 --> 01:00:03,003
Ipak, hvala ti.
- Nema na čemu.

762
01:00:03,680 --> 01:00:06,598
Igrajmo se u vodi.

763
01:00:06,724 --> 01:00:10,057
Ne možeš me nigdje naći.

764
01:00:10,227 --> 01:00:12,764
Reci Gdje je Arnie?

765
01:00:12,979 --> 01:00:16,099
Ne, idemo u vodu.
- Neću.

766
01:00:16,692 --> 01:00:18,815
Reci Gdje je Arnie?

767
01:00:18,986 --> 01:00:20,729
Reci.

768
01:00:20,861 --> 01:00:23,150
Gdje je Arnie?

769
01:00:23,280 --> 01:00:25,190
Ne možeš me naći.

770
01:00:25,365 --> 01:00:27,489
Reci opet.

771
01:00:27,952 --> 01:00:31,237
Moraš me tražiti
svuda okolo.

772
01:00:31,330 --> 01:00:34,034
Htjela sam da odemo plivati.

773
01:00:34,166 --> 01:00:36,917
Ne trudi se; boji se vode.

774
01:00:37,084 --> 01:00:39,124
Neće u vodu.

775
01:00:39,296 --> 01:00:41,418
Neću u vodu.

776
01:00:43,131 --> 01:00:45,920
Hoćeš ti u vodu?
- Neću.

777
01:00:47,094 --> 01:00:48,469
Zašto?

778
01:00:51,431 --> 01:00:54,800
Bojiš se ući
u vodu? - Ne.

779
01:00:55,435 --> 01:00:57,972
Siguran si?
- Jesam.

780
01:00:58,103 --> 01:00:59,646
Boji se.

781
01:00:59,939 --> 01:01:02,180
Bojiš se, Gilberte?

782
01:01:02,941 --> 01:01:05,147
Dobro, što želiš vidjeti?

783
01:01:06,445 --> 01:01:08,685
Želiš da se smočim?

784
01:01:08,863 --> 01:01:11,650
Da malo prskam?

785
01:01:15,243 --> 01:01:17,035
Još malo.

786
01:01:19,164 --> 01:01:21,286
Ovo hoćeš?

787
01:01:22,500 --> 01:01:24,658
Ovo hoćeš, ha?

788
01:01:25,002 --> 01:01:26,829
Zadovoljna?

789
01:01:32,718 --> 01:01:36,383
Reci što želiš. Što
ti prvo padne na pamet.

790
01:01:40,058 --> 01:01:41,765
Onda, što želiš?

791
01:01:43,561 --> 01:01:44,972
Brže!

792
01:01:45,520 --> 01:01:47,513
Želim nešto novo...

793
01:01:49,357 --> 01:01:52,275
Kuću. Novu kuću
za moju obitelj.

794
01:01:55,696 --> 01:01:58,270
Želim da mama

795
01:01:58,449 --> 01:02:00,488
ide na aerobiku.

796
01:02:01,660 --> 01:02:03,403
Da Ellen odraste.

797
01:02:04,246 --> 01:02:06,237
Novi mozak za Arniea.

798
01:02:07,791 --> 01:02:09,201
Želim...

799
01:02:10,293 --> 01:02:12,084
Što želiš za sebe?

800
01:02:13,170 --> 01:02:14,712
Samo za sebe.

801
01:02:16,381 --> 01:02:18,255
Želim biti dobra osoba.

802
01:02:22,888 --> 01:02:25,129
Ne mogu...

803
01:02:26,515 --> 01:02:28,093
Gdje je Arnie?

804
01:02:31,479 --> 01:02:33,021
Arnie?

805
01:02:38,067 --> 01:02:41,685
Jeste li vidjeli
Arniea? - Nisam.

806
01:02:57,668 --> 01:02:58,783
Sranje!

807
01:03:14,891 --> 01:03:16,303
Idemo.

808
01:03:17,061 --> 01:03:18,768
Ovamo!

809
01:03:20,481 --> 01:03:23,684
Opet sam uspio!

810
01:03:27,362 --> 01:03:27,896
Idemo dolje...

811
01:03:28,071 --> 01:03:31,486
Držim ga, Jerry...
- Ide s nama u postaju.

812
01:03:32,116 --> 01:03:36,195
Neće se ponoviti...
- Upozorili smo te

813
01:03:36,370 --> 01:03:39,738
da će idući put biti
posljednji! - No krasno!

814
01:03:39,873 --> 01:03:42,660
Upalite sirene, može?

815
01:03:44,376 --> 01:03:46,001
Bravo, Gilberte!

816
01:03:48,172 --> 01:03:50,497
Jerry, budite nježni s njim.

817
01:03:50,632 --> 01:03:52,956
Bez brige.

818
01:03:56,511 --> 01:04:01,507
Upalite sirene, može?
Sirene, može?

819
01:04:12,861 --> 01:04:14,438
Znam, šerife.

820
01:04:17,364 --> 01:04:19,025
Znam...

821
01:04:22,912 --> 01:04:24,369
Govnar!

822
01:04:24,871 --> 01:04:28,821
Zacijelo ga samo žele
naučiti pameti.

823
01:04:29,042 --> 01:04:30,701
Slažem se.

824
01:04:33,795 --> 01:04:35,291
Daj mi ogrtač.

825
01:04:37,007 --> 01:04:38,251
Što?

826
01:04:39,761 --> 01:04:41,170
Daj mi ogrtač.

827
01:04:43,722 --> 01:04:45,264
Daj mi ga!

828
01:04:57,067 --> 01:04:58,441
Krenimo.

829
01:05:10,746 --> 01:05:13,497
Tamo je barem na sigurnom.

830
01:05:13,665 --> 01:05:16,285
Tamo bar paze
na njega. - Šuti.

831
01:05:30,846 --> 01:05:32,969
Ostanite ovdje.
Odmah se vraćam.

832
01:05:33,265 --> 01:05:35,720
Mama, neka to
Gilbert sredi.

833
01:05:43,900 --> 01:05:46,307
Jerry, molim te...

834
01:05:46,402 --> 01:05:48,027
Pričekajte vani.

835
01:05:48,154 --> 01:05:50,775
Moraš ga pustiti.
- Niste na redu.

836
01:05:52,325 --> 01:05:55,076
Ne razumijete...
- Slušaj.

837
01:05:55,285 --> 01:05:59,910
Ništa neću učiniti
dok ne... - Jerry!

838
01:06:03,042 --> 01:06:04,370
Jerry!

839
01:06:09,673 --> 01:06:11,546
Jerry!

840
01:06:19,098 --> 01:06:20,841
Jerry...

841
01:06:21,016 --> 01:06:23,139
došla sam po sina.

842
01:06:27,981 --> 01:06:32,523
Moraš popuniti
neke obrasce... - Ne!

843
01:06:32,610 --> 01:06:35,183
Postupak zahtijeva...
- Hoću svoga sina.

844
01:06:35,321 --> 01:06:38,938
Bonnie, moraš...
- Daj mi sina!

845
01:06:50,918 --> 01:06:53,409
Dođi. Ideš doma.

846
01:06:55,631 --> 01:06:58,833
Sunce moje, slobodan si.

847
01:07:00,176 --> 01:07:03,296
Zlato, nemoj mi
to više raditi.

848
01:07:03,429 --> 01:07:05,088
Obećaj mi.

849
01:07:05,264 --> 01:07:08,632
Mama...
- Slobodan si.

850
01:07:08,767 --> 01:07:10,475
Idemo doma.

851
01:07:18,568 --> 01:07:20,109
Gle!

852
01:07:32,830 --> 01:07:35,368
Zato joj treba štap...!

853
01:08:22,583 --> 01:08:26,830
Mama, nisu htjeli
upaliti svjetla.

854
01:08:29,381 --> 01:08:32,003
Nisu upalili svjetla.

855
01:08:37,680 --> 01:08:41,262
Vidi me!

856
01:08:42,518 --> 01:08:46,218
Skrivam se. Reci
Gdje je Arnie?

857
01:08:46,521 --> 01:08:49,190
Reci...
- Arnie, dolje!

858
01:08:53,236 --> 01:08:58,063
Gilberte, nađi me.
Gdje je Arnie?

859
01:09:03,286 --> 01:09:06,203
To je moja mama. Moja mama.

860
01:09:08,040 --> 01:09:12,453
Gilberte, dođi se
igrati sa mnom.

861
01:09:29,184 --> 01:09:33,975
Tvoja je majka vrlo
hrabro postupila, zar ne?

862
01:09:37,525 --> 01:09:41,024
Voljela bih je upoznati.
- Ne, ne bi.

863
01:09:45,574 --> 01:09:47,613
Kamo idete odavde?

864
01:10:25,401 --> 01:10:27,938
Voljela bih upoznati
tvoju majku.

865
01:10:37,245 --> 01:10:41,740
Nadajući se uskrsnuću
i vječnome životu,

866
01:10:41,915 --> 01:10:45,913
predajemo Ti, Gospodine,
brata našega Kena Carvera,

867
01:10:46,085 --> 01:10:49,668
i tijelo njegovo
vraćamo zemlji.

868
01:10:49,798 --> 01:10:52,715
Što prah je bilo,

869
01:10:52,884 --> 01:10:55,884
u prah će se vratiti.

870
01:10:57,888 --> 01:11:00,924
Bog ga blagoslovio.

871
01:11:01,016 --> 01:11:05,096
Bože, obasjaj mu lice
i daj mu milost,

872
01:11:05,271 --> 01:11:09,978
budi blag i daj
mu vječni pokoj.

873
01:11:11,359 --> 01:11:16,269
Isuse, svojom si smrću
nama podario život;

874
01:11:16,362 --> 01:11:19,400
daj nama, slugama
svojim, vjeru

875
01:11:19,532 --> 01:11:22,106
da te slijedimo...

876
01:11:23,036 --> 01:11:24,744
Gledajte!

877
01:11:26,580 --> 01:11:28,573
Gle što dolazi!

878
01:11:28,750 --> 01:11:30,871
Gledajte što dolazi!
...vratio se iz mrtvih...

879
01:11:31,169 --> 01:11:35,710
veliki pastir...
- Super je! Gilberte!

880
01:11:35,922 --> 01:11:38,877
To je Burger Barn!

881
01:11:39,008 --> 01:11:43,469
Gilberte, gle!
Burger Barn!

882
01:11:43,637 --> 01:11:47,966
...nađi utjehu u
Isusu Kristu. Amen.

883
01:11:53,021 --> 01:11:55,772
Uzmite što god želite.

884
01:11:55,940 --> 01:11:59,106
Uzmite si bombone
ako hoćete.

885
01:11:59,902 --> 01:12:04,398
Ja ću nešto s mentolom.
- Volite žvakaće?

886
01:12:04,531 --> 01:12:05,907
Volite žvakaće?

887
01:12:06,032 --> 01:12:09,068
Ja volim. Ove su dobre.

888
01:12:09,160 --> 01:12:11,781
Uzmi si. Uzmi.

889
01:12:12,162 --> 01:12:15,745
Uzmi. Hoćeš i ti?

890
01:12:16,000 --> 01:12:20,293
Idemo u Saint Louis. Ne
mogu ostati u onoj kući.

891
01:12:23,047 --> 01:12:25,584
Doista mi je žao...

892
01:12:28,011 --> 01:12:31,213
Mama će platiti. Vi idite van.

893
01:12:35,476 --> 01:12:37,931
Svi misle da sam
ga ja ubila.

894
01:12:40,229 --> 01:12:41,688
A ti?

895
01:12:43,191 --> 01:12:44,566
Ne.

896
01:12:53,032 --> 01:12:54,692
Nedostaje mi.

897
01:12:58,663 --> 01:13:00,122
A i ne...

898
01:13:00,664 --> 01:13:02,491
Malo da, malo ne.

899
01:13:17,471 --> 01:13:19,428
Onda, Gilberte,

900
01:13:20,473 --> 01:13:22,134
što će biti s tobom?

901
01:13:23,726 --> 01:13:26,727
Vjerojatno ću...

902
01:13:26,938 --> 01:13:28,597
Nisi razmišljao o tome.

903
01:13:29,899 --> 01:13:33,399
Jadni Gilbert. Prikliješten.

904
01:13:33,944 --> 01:13:37,776
Brineš se za sve,
samo ne za sebe.

905
01:13:37,865 --> 01:13:41,149
Mama će odmah doći, dušo.

906
01:13:46,163 --> 01:13:48,370
Što se tiče mojih sinova...

907
01:13:48,540 --> 01:13:52,408
Ako budu imalo poput tebe...

908
01:13:56,255 --> 01:13:57,501
Bog.

909
01:14:08,516 --> 01:14:13,593
Bilo bi lijepo
da budu poput tebe.

910
01:14:31,120 --> 01:14:32,614
Prepuštam ti ga.

911
01:14:44,256 --> 01:14:46,462
Hoće li ti nedostajati?

912
01:14:54,266 --> 01:14:55,677
Dobro.

913
01:16:24,596 --> 01:16:25,924
Onda?

914
01:16:26,639 --> 01:16:27,838
Što misliš?

915
01:16:30,434 --> 01:16:33,851
Super. - Ha?

916
01:16:34,772 --> 01:16:36,432
Kušajte frape.

917
01:16:40,319 --> 01:16:42,277
Pravo mlijeko.

918
01:16:42,946 --> 01:16:44,773
Pravo.

919
01:16:56,000 --> 01:17:00,127
Čestitam! Super je.
- Baš ti hvala. - Što je?

920
01:17:00,378 --> 01:17:03,663
Morao si ovime doći?!
Svima ćeš pokvariti tek!

921
01:17:03,881 --> 01:17:05,624
Ti si Mike, točno?

922
01:17:05,759 --> 01:17:07,300
Hoćeš doći sutra
na moju zabavu?

923
01:17:07,426 --> 01:17:09,751
Navršit ću 18 godina.

924
01:17:09,929 --> 01:17:13,877
I ti možeš doći,
iako te ne poznajem.

925
01:17:14,975 --> 01:17:18,675
Drago mi je što ste
došli u ovolikom broju.

926
01:17:18,811 --> 01:17:22,939
Danas započinje
novo doba za Endoru,

927
01:17:23,024 --> 01:17:24,647
za Burger Barn

928
01:17:24,817 --> 01:17:27,568
i za sve vas, nadam se.

929
01:17:27,694 --> 01:17:32,819
Želimo sa svima vama
ostvariti dobar odnos,

930
01:17:32,990 --> 01:17:35,446
dugotrajan.

931
01:17:35,659 --> 01:17:38,660
U vrijeme kad mnoge
stvari propadaju,

932
01:17:38,829 --> 01:17:42,743
Endora je Burger
Barnu pružila šansu.

933
01:17:42,874 --> 01:17:45,199
Nov dašak života...

934
01:17:45,877 --> 01:17:48,165
Popravila ga je.

935
01:17:48,296 --> 01:17:50,335
Kamper je popravljen.

936
01:17:50,798 --> 01:17:53,372
Sutra odlazimo.

937
01:18:36,505 --> 01:18:40,752
Dođi sutra na moju
zabavu. - Dobro.

938
01:18:49,518 --> 01:18:51,556
Dakle, pozvana sam.

939
01:19:03,695 --> 01:19:06,104
Želiš da dođem ili ne?

940
01:19:06,241 --> 01:19:09,158
Ako hoćeš, dođi.

941
01:19:13,372 --> 01:19:16,408
Dakle... to želiš?

942
01:19:22,422 --> 01:19:24,047
Moram ići.

943
01:19:28,051 --> 01:19:29,843
Čuvaj se.

944
01:19:38,435 --> 01:19:40,180
Zbogom, Arnie.

945
01:19:42,357 --> 01:19:46,305
Ne... - Moraš
se okupati.

946
01:19:48,611 --> 01:19:50,105
Arnie...

947
01:19:51,073 --> 01:19:52,613
Arnie...

948
01:19:53,074 --> 01:19:54,568
Dečki...

949
01:19:55,701 --> 01:19:58,074
Moraš se okupati, Arnie.

950
01:20:02,123 --> 01:20:04,615
Moraš! Rođendan ti je!

951
01:20:06,586 --> 01:20:09,456
Arnie... Kvragu!

952
01:20:09,630 --> 01:20:11,753
Ne, Arnie!

953
01:20:13,133 --> 01:20:14,841
Zaboga...

954
01:20:15,969 --> 01:20:18,542
Drugu ne stignem napraviti!

955
01:20:21,640 --> 01:20:23,763
Moramo imati tortu.

956
01:20:55,421 --> 01:20:56,880
Izvolite?

957
01:20:58,924 --> 01:21:01,758
Došao sam po tortu
na ime Grape.

958
01:21:01,927 --> 01:21:03,636
Da, gotova je.

959
01:21:05,513 --> 01:21:09,213
Izvolite. 19.75.

960
01:21:27,283 --> 01:21:28,777
Makni se.

961
01:21:28,867 --> 01:21:31,868
Što je to?
- Iznenađenje. Pusti.

962
01:21:31,995 --> 01:21:35,079
Što je u kutiji? - Takneš
li je, ubit ću te!

963
01:21:35,248 --> 01:21:37,157
Nisi normalan.

964
01:21:37,375 --> 01:21:39,997
Ja ću vas gledati iz kuće.

965
01:21:40,127 --> 01:21:44,920
